1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on image processing applications such as image inpainting and multi-focus image fusion, which are typical tasks in computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a novel stochastic gradient descent version of the Local Block Coordinate Descent algorithm for training the convolutional filters, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the Convolutional Sparse Coding (CSC) model, which is a signal processing technique that involves compressing and decompressing signals. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image processing tasks, which are a part of multimedia applications. 
5. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for the CSC model, which involves numerical computations and optimization techniques.
